'''Greece''' participated in the '''Eurovision Song Contest 1976''' in [[The Hague]]. [[Mariza Koch]] represented Greece with the song "[[Panagia Mou, Panagia Mou]]". She scored 20 points (the highest being 8 from France) placing 13th.

